parameters:
Goat of the Bulk Brigade: Welcome, my comrades! I am proud
to have fought alongside you against the dragons at the
heart of the empire.

Goat of the Bulk Brigade: In the history of the renowned
Bulk Brigade, you all will become the idols of warriors!

\CL 【The Aftermath of Goat from the Bulk Brigade】There was a
division between the reformist faction led by Goat and the
conservative faction led by the elders, but through
persistent persuasion, a new system was established with
Goat at its center.

\CL In the Third Tarasa War instigated by King Rex, they
fought valiantly in unfamiliar naval battles and were feared
by both enemies and allies alike.

\CL Thanks to their achievements, Goat from the Bulk Brigade
will be talked about as the strongest for a long time.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

You won't be able to come back, but are you really leaving
the mansion?
Clea (We haven't talked yet, have we?)

3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Clea: I learned about the ways of a warrior from Goats-san.
Although our positions are different, I hope to contribute
to the peace of the empire together.

Goats of the Bulk Gang: Peace in the empire... The era of
only looking out for Waldt has come to an end. I agree.

Goats of the Bulk Gang: I would like to have a serious match
with you, not in a half-hearted state like an ogre!

Mage Relm: Even in the empire that denies magic like Waldt,
the number of people who are gradually increasing is also
growing, right?

Goats of the Bulk Gang: Once something starts moving, it
cannot be stopped. However, there are things that we must
resist and protect.

Mage Relm: Yes, I also think so. I will keep it in mind as
the future Archmage.

Thief Nora: I will join the mercenary group in the Waldt
region!

Goats of the Bulk Gang: Hahaha, that's great! While working
as a mercenary, you should come here to train or something!

Thief Nora: Yes, thank you very much! Since Waldt has
delicious food, I will come to visit again!

Priestess Sophia: Since then, have there been any people who
have transformed into ogres through their interactions with
everyone and experienced growth?

Goats of the Bulk Gang: Thanks to you all, there are many
who are opposed to changes in rituals and the Imiserinos
faith.

Priestess Sophia: Only the Goats can resolve that. May the
goddess Imiserinos bless the Bulk Gang.
